ratios.Average Cost (Inventories) = Industry.inventories.fg.val, Industry.inventories.fg.vol
ratios.Capital Ratio = Industry.capital, Industry.liabilities
ratios.Capacity Utilization = Industry.workforce, Industry.capacity
ratios.Cash to Wages Ratio = Industry.cash, Industry.wageBill
